  "response": "Several payment gateways are popular in India:\n\n1. Razorpay\n- Best for online businesses\n- Supports multiple payment methods\n- Low transaction fees\n- Easy integration\n\n2. Paytm Payment Gateway\n- Large user base\n- Multiple payment options\n- Quick settlement\n- Good for small businesses\n\n3. CCAvenue\n- Oldest payment gateway in India\n- Supports international transactions\n- Wide range of payment modes\n- Suitable for medium to large businesses\n\n4. PhonePe Payment Gateway\n- High transaction volume\n- UPI-enabled\n- Low transaction charges\n- Good mobile integration\n\n5. PayU\n- Multiple payment methods\n- International transactions\n- Quick setup\n- Robust security features\n\n6. Bill Desk\n- Trusted by many large corporations\n- Multiple payment options\n- High security standards\n- Good customer support\n\nEach gateway has pros and cons, so the best choice depends on your specific business requirements, transaction volume, budget, and target audience.\n\nFactors to consider:\n- Transaction fees\n- Integration complexity\n- Payment method support\n- Settlement time\n- Customer support\n- Security features\n\nRecommendation: Compare features and get quotes from multiple gateways before deciding.",
